
This directory contains the tools to build the RL02 distribution kit.

getstat
	- program to get file sizes and types.

ifempty.sh
	- shell script to find empty directories.

createmd
	- program to create shell script which will build tar format disks.

rldist.sh
	- shell script to run getstat, ifempty.sh and createmd.

TO RUN IT DO THE FOLLOWING:

su
	- become super user so that getstat can stat all of the files.

rldist.sh [/path]
	- Where /path is the path where the master pack is mounted.

cd /path
makerldist
